-- Lehman Japan to file for court protection: source
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2008 7:19pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/15/us-lehman-japan-idUSTKB00300620080915

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Japan Inc, a Japanese unit of Lehman Brothers Holdings, will file for court protection from creditors in Tokyo, a source said on Tuesday. 

 The U.S. investment bank filed for bankruptcy protection in the United States on Monday. (Reporting by  Taiga Uranaka ; Editing by  Rodney Joyce )